# Reveal.js - Presentaciones Workalógico

## Configuración Base Obligatoria

### Dimensiones del Viewport
```javascript
Reveal.initialize({
  width: 1280,
  height: 720,
  margin: 0.1,
  minScale: 0.2,
  maxScale: 1.2,
  center: true
});
```

### Transiciones Fluidas (Fluidity Overhaul)
```javascript
transition: 'slide',
transitionSpeed: 'slow',
backgroundTransition: 'fade'
```

